ArtyTorrent Pack 44-Hip Hop Drum Loops 100-109 bpm-WAV samples
--------------------------------------------------------------

A variety of Hip Hop loops that can also be used for RnB and Funk tracks.
The tempo ranges from 100-109 bpm.

Torrent contains 4 RAR files with 150 loops.
-------------------------------------------
Elab Hip Hop 100 (10 loops)
Misc Hip Hop 100-107 (33 loops)
Zero-G Hip Hop 100 (67 loops)
Zero-G Hip Hop 105 (40 loops)

As usual, all samples have been normalized and acidized and are 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the approx bpm in the filenames.

The samples are from a variety of sources including CDs produced by Elab, East-West and Zero-G.
